title: #92Noon! Zimmer Presser/Florio/Zimmer coldcall/Talkers
description: #92Noon Kicks off with Mike Zimmer's season-ending presser at Winter Park, Mike Florio makes his weekly stop, we begin to analyze the upcoming Vikings QB conundrum, Mike Zimmer calls into the show on his way to the airport, and more!
